    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……\n……トレーナー、もう一度、最初からお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "huf‚ huf……\n…Trainer‚ could you please start from the beginning again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.0000000953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そろそろ一度、休憩を入れた方がいいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe we should take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "endTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それに今だって、直すところなんてないくらいだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And even now‚ it was practically perfect‚ there's nothing to fix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "endTime": 14.828347365099999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません\n一回目のサビ直前の転調で、半テンポ遅れました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry.\nI was half a beat late on the key change right before the first chorus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0333333333,
      "endTime": 20.5025852522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
