      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "練習で完璧に仕上げられなければ\n本番で完璧なパフォーマンスなんて出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we can't perfect it in practice‚\nwe can't give a perfect performance on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "endTime": 34.564762052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "トレーナー、もう一度お願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trainer‚ one more time‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7666666667,
      "endTime": 37.6666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、kanaのステップ\n念入りにチェックしてくれると助かりま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ could you\ncheck my steps carefully‚ please~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8666666667,
      "endTime": 43.286281267899994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
