      "text": "今日もライブお疲れ様\n差し入れをいただいたから、ここに置いておくわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work on the live today.\nWe got some treats‚ so I'll leave them here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5666666667,
      "endTime": 57.6064494712,
      "sfxList": [
        {
