      "text": "……最近はコスメ一緒に展開するブランドも増えたわね\nどのくらいなら採算取れるんだろ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…There are more and more brands collaborating on cosmetics these days.\nI wonder how much they make from it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "endTime": 71.41472864219999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8799.999999999996,
          "startTime": 72.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
