    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "『今日のライブは、ちょっとしたハプニングが』……\nうーん、あんまり面白くないな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's live‚ there was a little mishap…\nHmm‚ this isn't very interesting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "endTime": 80.5210520426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "毎日毎日、SNSに投稿してると\nkanaってば作家になった気がしてくるよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Posting on social media every day‚\nmakes me feel like a writer~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7333333333,
      "endTime": 88.1307016967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
