      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "（二人ともこちらを振り向きもしないわね……）\n（でも、これでいい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They're not even looking at me…)\n(But this is fine.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1666666667,
      "endTime": 95.9520833334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "（ようやく、この子達が熱心になってくれたのだもの）\n（勝てるなら他には何も望まないわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They're finally motivated.)\n(As long as we can win‚ I don't want anything else.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1666666667,
      "endTime": 102.6365241686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そして、VENUSグランプリから九ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――And nine months after the Venus Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333333333,
      "endTime": 106.66666666660001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
