    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-prekan001.m4a",
      "text": "前から君達に頼まれていた\n『STROBOLIGHTS』との再戦が決まったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About what you asked me before‚\nthe rematch with STROBOLIGHTS has been decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6333333333,
      "endTime": 112.7933333079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-prekan002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4ともなるとなかなか勝負を受けてくれなくてね\n取り付けるのには苦労したよ、わははは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was difficult to get BIG4 to agree to a match‚\nit took a lot of effort to arrange this. Wahahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113,
      "endTime": 120.1533333253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3666666667,
      "endTime": 122.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_05-prekan003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきメディアにもプレスリリースを流しておいたよ\n『BIG4への、因縁のリベンジバトル』ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just sent out a press release to the media.\n\"A Revenge Battle Fueled by Bad Blood against BIG4\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3666666667,
      "endTime": 129.9133333607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
